Big update ahoy! : We ve been working hard on improving Reflectly with the continuous goal of building the best possible experience around journaling and reflection. With this update we re happy to introduce a new concept: the Today page ! The Today page is a central starting point in the app that contains a collection of daily questions motivational content and exercises to help you reflect on life. The page changes every day with new experiences for you to try out so be sure to check back regularly! We d love your thoughts on this new direction and how we can improve your journaling experience. Let us know what you think by leaving a review or send us a message to let us know! :

Huge update ahoy! After working closely with our amazing users and listening to all your feedback we re now shipping the biggest update ever to Reflectly! This update contains: An entirely new way to journal revolving around a timeline of your life Daily reflections: gain some perspective on life with a new curated question every day Add multiple entries per day any time you want Select as many activities and feelings as you wish with your journal entries New statistics graphs to better help you understand how you re feeling Upload images directly to your timeline A greatly improved offline experience ... and much much more! This is just the beginning we have so many great features to come very soon. We hope you love these new additions to Reflectly. Tell us what you think by leaving a review! :

Reflectly v2.0 is here! Our biggest update ever: We ve teamed up with some of the leading self care and mental health experts to bring you Audio Reflections . They re little golden nuggets of knowledge that prompt the reflection process and give a little perspective on the larger picture in life. You can unlock a completely new one every day at the end of each story you create. Try it completely for free with our 7 day free trial cancel at any time if you re not digging the content! : We ve also added the ability to lock your app with a Biometric Lock! Oh did we mention color themes We ve also included 6 beautiful themes for you to customize your Reflectly experience which we ll continue adding on. Tell us what you think by leaving a review! : Version also includes various bug fixes and minor improvements.
